reviewText: This series is a very light hearted, funny one that's highly enjoyable.  ***Sadly, they did Not release the entire series.***  Only 4 or 5 episodes were put on 4 DVD releases.  But, for what it is, this is a very good DVD, ... just don't expect it to be the full Season.

reviewText: "That's So Raven" has become a phenomenon for Disney Channel, and quickly became more popular than the ever-annoying series "Lizzie McGuire". The show is hilarious. It's about a girl named Raven, who has psychic powers. She has two friends, Eddie and Chelsea. Raven sees glimpses of the future, which she often tries to prevent, but ends up causing the vision to come true. If you're looking for enough laughs to give you a six-pack, buy this DVD.
summary: The best new comedy on Disney Channel
